text: Cameo Kirby is a 1914 American silent drama movie directed by Oscar Apfel and is the first version of the 1909 play of the same name by Booth Tarkington and Harry Leon Wilson. It stars Dustin Farnum, Fred Montague, James Neill, Jode Mullally, Winifred Kingston, Dick Le Reno, Ernest Joy and was distributed by Paramount Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1914 drama movies Category:American silent movies Category:American drama movies Category:Movies based on books Category:Paramount Pictures movies Category:Movies directed by Oscar Apfel
